key_conclusion:
Playing God is written in the key of E Minor.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the 2nd most popular key among Minor keys and     the 8th most popular  among all keys. The three most important chords, built off the 1st, 4th and 5th scale degrees are all minor chords (E minor, A minor, and B minor).
